Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.58,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,461)}Em troca, seja meu servo {manga 874 title}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:37.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:38.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esperem um momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:43.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi isso que aconteceu na\N festa do chá-chocolate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,F-Foram os Chapéu de Palha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.57,0:01:47.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, foi um desastre!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.50,0:01:50.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O casamento e o bolo \Nde casamento foram arruinados!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E a execução dos Vinsmoke falhou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:57.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para piorar, Bege nos traiu \Ne conspirou para matar a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:59.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldito Bege...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:03.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu o respeitava por suas habilidades-noir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.54,0:02:08.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{\an8}Mas ainda não sabemos\N nada sobre a explosão.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:08.21,OPLetrerosInv,,0,0,0,,{\pos(915,365)}{\pos(392,490)\fscx95\fscy95\fad(500,0)}FAMÍLIA CHARLOTTE\NFILHA MAIS VELHA {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:15.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todos estavam no telhado, então\N se eles tivessem feito isso, seria um ato de suicídio.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É bastante improvável.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:21.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas resolvemos um mistério-moule.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:23.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Durante a festa do chá,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:28.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,todos os meios de comunicação\N pararam de funcionar-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:31.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Devem ter sido Bege e os outros.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:34.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Havia algo para relatar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:40.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, durante a festa do chá, os Piratas\N do Sol que estavam na costa leste...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.52,0:02:44.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fugiram-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:45.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pekoms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:50.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Todos os piratas tritões \Nempacotaram e fugiram!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:54.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso Jinbe pôde agir assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:02.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...deixou os Piratas da Big Mom e\N se juntou aos Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:04.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:07.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Jinbe renunciou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:08.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deve ter sido por isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele sabia que mama iria \Ncontra seus amigos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:17.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso adiou sua \Nsaída temporariamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:20.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...para permitir que \Nseus amigos fugissem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:23.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito próprio de Jinbe\N pensar em algo tão inteligente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Katakuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:30.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossas tropas já estão perseguindo\N o Chapéu de Palha e Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:31.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:34.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E outro esquadrão está invadindo Germa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.64,0:03:36.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brûlée, venha comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:40.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Claro, irmãozinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:43.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você poderia matar o Chapéu \Nde Palha e os outros?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vou perdoá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:49.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles me usaram como escrava...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:52.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e me forçaram a ajudar no\N plano deles para matar a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:55.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso que vou fazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:59.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou pegar a cabeça do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:03.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Percebi que é necessário eliminá-lo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:06.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...antes que ele se torne uma \Nverdadeira ameaça para a mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:25.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:26.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam da cidade!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:28.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Smoothie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Corram o mais longe possível!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:35.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Em um momento como esse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo, Smoothie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:40.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:54.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que agora...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:58.61,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(537,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}REINO GERMA {843 15:13:84}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não consigo entrar em contato com\N Judge-sama nem com Ichiji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:04.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que diabos aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:06.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Os Piratas da Big Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde está o bolo de casamento?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:44.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A doença da comida da rainha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:48.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Outro ataque seguido, e\N depois de tão pouco tempo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:56.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela lembrou do bolo de casamento\Ndestruído que não pôde comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que a mama tem na mão?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já é tarde.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão Ópera!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:34.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Resista!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:36.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela tirou sua expectativa de vida?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:43.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nosso irmão Ópera se\N interpôs para tentar detê-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:47.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ninguém se aproxime da mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Precisamos fazer algo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:07.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depressa, gente!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Logo estarão nos perseguindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:27.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está em cima do Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:29.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se ache tanto!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não tem problema!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.85,Sanji in Love,,0,0,0,,Porque a Nami-san é linda!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Linda e delicada...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida de que os Piratas \Nda Big Mom nos perseguirão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Precisamos nos apressar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:51.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A rota mais curta para chegar ao Sunny é\N seguir por aqui e atravessar o Bosque Sedutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:58.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês todos sabem o que fazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:05.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A única forma de parar a doença\N da comida da mama é dar a ela o que ela quer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que precisamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...é de um bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:13.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde está o grande chefe de cozinha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.25,0:08:16.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele é o único que pode\N preparar o bolo novamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:19.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Streusen-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...nos salvou a vida,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:27.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,mas aterrissou muito mal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:36.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele vai precisar de vários dias\N para se recuperar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:42.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A este ritmo, Sweet City\N será destruída-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:46.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como vamos deter a mama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:52.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não podemos deixar que ela destrua a capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:06.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde está?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:10.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele teve uma ideia, hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:15.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como era de se esperar\N do Perospero-sama-gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:18.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O bolo de casamento...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:24.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...ainda existe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tínhamos um de reserva, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão Peros!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.51,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Irmão Peros!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:41.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-Ele é feito de ingredientes \Nselecionados cuidadosamente...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:44.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E derrete na boca.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:49.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o melhor bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:56.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu queria que você o comesse, mas quem diria que os Chapéu de Palha o roubariam e fugiriam com ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:10:02.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles estão indo para o sudoeste\N e tentando escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:05.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:08.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de casamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:12.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles o têm-Lambida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.91,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Parece que ela está me ouvindo um pouco.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:20.62,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Se ela perseguir o Chapéu de Palha,\N mataremos dois coelhos com uma cajadada só!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.92,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ele conseguirá convencê-la?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:43.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se você estiver mentindo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:48.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,vai pagar com sua expectativa de vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:11.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:24.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso não é bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:29.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que ela mate os Chapéu de\N Palha, eles não têm o bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:30.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que eu faço?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:32.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pensei que tinha dado certo, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:40.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando a mama voltar, eu vou morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas você ganhou algum tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:46.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Devemos aproveitar para preparar\N o bolo ou será o fim desta ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, é impossível.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.48,0:11:51.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pense bem, Smoothie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:58.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quantos dias você acha que o Streusen, nosso grande chefe de cozinha, levou para preparar aquele bolo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:04.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já não temos mais os ingredientes raros que\N conseguimos roubando de outros países!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:08.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E quem o preparou está inconsciente!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele não pode fazer um bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:18.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E além disso, a mama não provou o bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então agora devemos dar a ela...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.00,0:12:28.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O bolo superdelicioso que ela\N imaginou, mas nunca provou!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:33.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem poderia preparar algo assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:36.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso não está indo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,No mínimo, será o fim desta ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:42.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que acontecerá depois\N disso é uma incógnita.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês querem minha ajuda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, Pudding-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:14.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O bolo de casamento era um\N bolo chiffon de chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:19.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu posso fazer um chocolate \Ntão bom quanto o do grande chefe de cozinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:24.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E minha irmã Chiffon é \Nespecialista em bolos chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:28.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Juntas, podemos fazer esse bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:30.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você tem certeza, Pudding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:36.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas Chiffon é a esposa\N do Bege, nosso inimigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:39.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela fará o que eu disser!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A Pudding má apareceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:42.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:44.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding-sama está agindo\N como uma delinquente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:49.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A verdade é que os \Ningredientes do bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:53.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...foram armazenados temporariamente \Nem Chocolat Town, na Ilha Cacau,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,na entrada do nosso território.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:59.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então ainda temos\N esses ingredientes raros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão Peros!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:05.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depois que a mama eliminar os \NChapéu de Palha, leve-a para Chocolat Town!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.25,0:14:08.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu vou acalmá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:11.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tem certeza?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você nos salvou, Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji me insultou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:20.64,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Que olho lindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se a mama puder se livrar deles,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:27.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,eu devo recompensá-la.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:33.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere e verá!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:35.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:38.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:41.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu coração deu um salto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:44.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Alguma garota bonita deve estar falando de mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Bosque Sedutor está à vista!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:49.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos entrar naquele bosque de novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos ficar bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, o que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:58.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, chega, Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:00.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Kin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,D-Dói!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.20,0:15:05.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Minha sutura-ju dói, Lady Tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:07.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas logo tudo estará unido.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.48,0:15:13.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,D-Dói!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:16.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me toque com mais delicadeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:21.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:21.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não acredito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:22.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como é possível?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:26.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:32.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está vivo, Kingbaum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nos encontramos de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:38.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Árvore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,N-Não...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se aproximem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:50.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão pagar por isso, malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:54.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lady Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não olhe para trás, siga em frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:01.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:02.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:06.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami, eles não tinham tirado\N a Vivre Card da Lola de você?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, uma parte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:09.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cortei ao meio, por precaução.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nada mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:13.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele é muito rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:17.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como ele é o chefe do Bosque Sedutor,\N pode atravessar o bosque diretamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:20.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Avance na velocidade máxima\N em direção ao Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:21.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:24.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês são uma praga-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:27.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sumam já do país-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:29.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você disse algo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:33.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obedeça a Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:42.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nossos alvos estão próximos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:43.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Derrubem eles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:47.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.20,0:16:50.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Olhem atrás, são inimigos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:52.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ao ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:55.54,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:57.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depressa, Kingbaum!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já estou indo o mais rápido possível-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:02.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se te pegarem, vou tirar a sutura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.52,0:17:03.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:10.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Algo passou voando!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Essa voz...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:15.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.50,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:28.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:31.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me dê isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:43.70,Principio,,0,0,0,,Enquanto isso, no rio Juice, \Npróximo a Sweet City...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, estou vendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:50.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O rio Juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:53.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá está ancorado o Shark Submerge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Naquele rio, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:03.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O rio está cheio de chantilly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:06.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, que cheiro delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:13.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bom apetite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:15.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:21.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem diria que os escombros do Whole Cake Château desmoronado chegariam até aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Q-Que delícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:29.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, e agora o que fazemos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Chopper-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.17,0:18:38.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:48.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Temos que escapar da Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:51.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que ela está fazendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:52.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso, ela não parece...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...estar em sã consciência!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:56.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Será que é a doença da comida dela?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:19:00.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:02.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tire ela de cima de nós, Kingbaum!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:04.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é loucura-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:12.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Experimentem a lança de Elbaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Elbaf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:20.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela vai nos atacar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:33.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ikoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.54,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.54,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.54,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.54,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.54,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Nação soberana.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:23.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:29.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece a técnica dos gigantes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.67,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Hakoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.67,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Hakoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:38.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.89,0:20:41.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kingbaum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.19,0:20:46.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me perdoe-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:50.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me forçaram-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:53.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela vai nos atacar de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:56.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos descer para lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kingbaum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.53,0:20:59.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem era aquela garota?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:00.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sua namorada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:05.53,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Não, chega, Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.09,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,{}Você está bem, Kin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:09.79,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Kin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.64,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Lady Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:15.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E-É minha noiva-ju.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.03,0:21:18.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, noiva?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:23.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Prometemos passar o resto \Nde nossas vidas juntos-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sobreviva!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:33.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sobreviva por ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:35.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Para vê-la novamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:45.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:48.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não posso morrer aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:50.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Corra, Kingbaum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:54.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma nova vida com ela te espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:57.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um futuro cheio de amor te aguarda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:02.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lady Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:04.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:06.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.70,0:22:08.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como era de esperar da Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:11.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me dê o bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:13.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, agora sou eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:14.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.27,0:22:16.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tenho um plano!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:18.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:19.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você vai fazer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:23.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:25.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Black Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:33.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nuvens amam relâmpagos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:35.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ikoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:42.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:44.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele comeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:44.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:47.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que delícia, que delícia!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:51.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,702)}Ah, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:51.41,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1018,702)}Ah, mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:55.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo, Zeus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:00.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É inútil, ele está distraído!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:04.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles estão fugindo para\N o Bosque Sedutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.96,0:23:11.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,No bosque teremos a vantagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:16.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Porque o Kingbaum...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:19.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...é o chefe do bosque!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:21.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o Kingbaum-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:24.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kingbaum-sama está vindo para cá!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:27.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.90,0:23:34.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.45,0:23:35.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Caramba!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.60,0:23:38.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nada mal, árvore gigante.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:39.15,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saia da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:42.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saia da frente, saia da frente-ju-ju-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:51.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.43,0:23:53.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.42,0:23:55.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos direto para a costa, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:58.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seu plano foi incrível! {english line: "That was an amazing plan, Nami!" maybe add the nami part?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.59,0:24:01.64,Sanji in Love,,0,0,0,,Como era de esperar da Nami-swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:09.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Contanto que a Big Mom não suba em Zeus, nós podemos fugir deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:11.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele se chama Zeus?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:15.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, essa nuvem carrega a alma da mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.24,0:24:16.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, sou Zeus.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.94,0:24:18.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zeus-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.45,0:24:19.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.40,0:24:20.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele está aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.16,0:24:21.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cuidado!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:22.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele é forte!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:25.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, essas nuvens de trovão...!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.89,0:24:27.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me dê mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.20,0:24:29.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.61,0:24:33.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Black Ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.35,0:24:38.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que como nuvens\N de trovão tão intensas e macias!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:40.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você tem mais?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.64,0:24:43.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, são gostosas?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.97,0:24:50.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É muito macio!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:54.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Me dê mais, mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.28,0:24:55.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, nuvem!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:24:57.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esqueça isso e me deixe montar em você!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.35,0:24:59.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Impossível.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.37,0:25:02.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só a mama, que me deu parte\N de sua alma, pode montar em mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.98,0:25:04.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.04,0:25:05.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é uma nuvem comum.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.46,0:25:07.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Uma nuvem?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.53,0:25:10.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Zeus, então...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.95,0:25:14.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você seria meu servo?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.55,0:25:15.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.63,0:25:17.39,Sanji in Love,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.39,0:25:19.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não estava perguntando a você.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.63,0:25:23.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Assim você comerá Black Balls todos os dias!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.32,0:25:24.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.13,0:25:25.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.49,0:25:27.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que eu faço? O que eu faço?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.74,0:25:30.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não guarda lealdade à sua chefe?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.34,0:25:36.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você pode se tornar uma nuvem enorme de trovão capaz de cobrir todo o céu, certo?! {english line: "I noticed earlier that you're able to completely cover the sky!" i also hear nami saying "sora"}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.29,0:25:38.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.66,0:25:40.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.80,0:25:44.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que me elogiam assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.14,0:26:10.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,M-Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.35,0:26:12.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.10,0:26:15.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bosque Sedutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.94,0:26:19.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Detenham-nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.37,0:26:31.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.43,0:26:33.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama ficou brava!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.28,0:26:39.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O bosque voltou a ficar irritado.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.80,0:26:43.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que não os chutamos para afastá-los?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.68,0:26:45.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.21,0:26:50.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Enquanto faz isso, você vai se perder \Ne não vai saber onde está!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.12,0:26:51.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.55,0:26:54.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Este bosque desorienta as pessoas.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.87,0:27:05.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Minhas ordens não se comparam \Ncom as da rainha!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.70,0:27:12.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.37,0:27:17.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lady Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.66,0:27:19.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.02,0:27:23.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Corra a toda velocidade pelo\N amor e seu futuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.34,0:27:26.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,São ordens da mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.59,0:27:27.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Detenham-nos!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.49,0:27:29.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saiam da frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.36,0:27:32.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não posso morrer aqui-ju!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.24,0:27:35.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que ele faz isso,\N Kingbaum-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.14,0:27:40.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você consegue, Kingbaum!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.54,0:27:46.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Segurem-se firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.40,0:27:47.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.09,0:27:49.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Árvore, não pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.63,0:27:52.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.96,0:27:55.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.03,0:28:20.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, que útil.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.33,0:28:25.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Queima.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.61,0:28:26.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.64,0:28:28.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.52,0:28:42.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É o Prometheus-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.03,0:28:44.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele está furioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.28,0:28:48.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, Kingbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.57,0:28:53.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você traiu a mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.01,0:28:57.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,P-Prometheus-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.88,0:29:00.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que calor!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.00,0:29:02.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Lá vem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.87,0:29:04.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele quer nos esmagar?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.67,0:29:06.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kingbaum, fuja!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.88,0:29:16.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kingbaum, corra!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.55,0:29:18.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sua prometida está esperando, não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.36,0:29:25.96,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Impossível, fujam!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.34,0:29:40.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Corra!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.48,0:29:41.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami, por aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.80,0:29:43.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.02,0:29:44.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles vão ser envolvidos!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.82,0:29:46.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.47,0:30:02.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Árvore!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.04,0:30:06.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Kingbaum...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.91,0:30:08.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.30,0:30:27.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.38,0:30:32.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde está Bege?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.91,0:30:34.99,Denden,,0,0,0,,Vamos alcançá-lo logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.99,0:30:37.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,1,,{\an8}Há um incêndio no Bosque Sedutor...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.50,0:30:39.96,OPLetreros,,0,0,170,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(532,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}SWEET CITY - A CAPITAL
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.86,0:30:39.96,Denden,,0,0,1,,{\an8}Achamos que a mama está lutando.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.90,0:30:42.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou falando do Mirro World.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.83,0:30:43.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Montd'Or!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.99,0:30:49.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Temos dez mil soldados para enviar a qualquer momento para qualquer lugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.10,0:30:49.35,OPLetreros,,0,1010,0,,{\fad(500,500)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(130,415)}MIRRO WORLD {PACE ONLY INFOBOX}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.92,0:30:53.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De acordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.20,0:30:54.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos em contato.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.88,0:30:56.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Doces.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.44,0:30:57.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Biscoitos.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.62,0:30:58.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nozes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.70,0:31:03.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que os navios dessas ilhas vigiem a costa sudoeste, onde está ancorado o navio dos Chapéus de Palha,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.97,0:31:06.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,e não permitam que zarpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.36,0:31:07.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.36,0:31:07.40,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.40,0:31:11.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Rodeá-los será a primeira barreira.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.65,0:31:16.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depois seguirão navios de bolo\N das ilhas Sabores e Licor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.84,0:31:20.53,Denden,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se e esperem no porto.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.53,0:31:24.05,Denden,,0,0,0,,Esperem os sinais de alerta\N telepáticos das lesmas marinhas. {in WCI2 14:28:05 these "lesmas marinhas" são mencionadas com outro nome}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.05,0:31:26.08,Denden,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.82,0:31:33.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pensem que poderão escapar da rede de vigilância das lesmas marinhas.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.12,0:31:38.13,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(532,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}COSTA SUDOESTE - SUNNY
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.13,0:31:40.11,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Há muita agitação no bosque.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.11,0:31:41.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.38,0:31:49.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mama está perseguindo eles, então\N é impossível que cheguem aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.97,0:31:51.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Supondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.66,0:31:55.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, por que os emboscamos?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.54,0:31:58.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por precaução.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.56,0:32:07.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles vêm nos tanques de bolo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.38,0:32:08.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.82,0:32:13.63,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estamos quase na costa!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.63,0:32:15.89,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles não vão nos alcançar!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.17,0:32:18.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmão Bege!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.65,0:32:19.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.65,0:32:20.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que susto!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.00,0:32:23.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding-sa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.13,0:32:24.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Digo, Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.53,0:32:27.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não terei piedade por você ser uma garota!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.10,0:32:29.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero falar com\N minha irmã Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.75,0:32:31.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixe-me vê-la, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.55,0:32:34.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmã Chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.85,0:32:35.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde você está?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.35,0:32:39.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.32,0:32:40.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por que você veio?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.54,0:32:41.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Irmã!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.73,0:32:45.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Preciso da sua ajuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.13,0:32:48.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mama está tendo outro ataque por causa da comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.28,0:32:51.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela quer um bolo de casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.43,0:32:54.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A doença da comida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.47,0:32:59.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, e o bolo de casamento é \Num bolo de chocolate chiffon!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.24,0:33:01.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você entende agora, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.79,0:33:07.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você precisa do meu bolo chiffon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.07,0:33:13.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, se combinarmos meu\N chocolate e seu bolo chiffon,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.46,0:33:17.33,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,teremos um bolo de\N casamento que agradará a mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.33,0:33:21.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se dermos a ela, pararemos\N sua doença da comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.05,0:33:30.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito, Pudding.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.73,0:33:34.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Assim como Lola, \Nvou deixar este lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.52,0:33:38.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me importo com o que aconteça \Ncom a mama ou com este país!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.47,0:33:39.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.70,0:33:41.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entenda isso e vá embora, Pudding!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.54,0:33:43.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.22,0:33:53.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu verdadeiro propósito...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.08,0:33:56.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...não é salvar a mama \Nou este país!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.75,0:34:04.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Preciso parar a mama logo...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.00,0:34:07.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não, ele...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.59,0:34:11.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e seus companheiros serão mortos!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.38,0:34:14.40,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTempos:\NGalaxy 9000,\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.65,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você procura...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.49,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.07,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.76,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:43.35,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e ondule-as...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:50.23,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.19,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.57,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.87,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para que futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.37,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.00,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você procura...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.22,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.55,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços imutáveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.85,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.64,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:33.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}já decidimos isso há muito tempo.
